The problem lies with the line:

    var list = $(&quot;.search-results li&quot;);

Which is not limited within each search result.

What you&#39;ll need to do is limit that line to within the searchResult:

    var list = $(&quot;.search-results li&quot;, searchResult);

Note that you may not also be selecting the correct button with the `#next` as well.

